race.comment: OUR BRAVE LINI (9) has been just behind the placegetters in town in both career outings to date and should find this assignment a touch easier. Lerena sticks in the irons following that last-start effort and can feature with natural improvement. HERALD ANGEL (3) resumes here but the form she showed in her first preparation was good enough for a race of this nature. Can play a big role from the inside alley. CHAMPAGNE TOWER (2) has placed two of three over this track and trip and gets some weight relief with the 3kg claim. Top-three candidate. ICYMISS (6) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown ability at the trials and won't need to be a superstar to be competitive against this lot. Keep very safe. LUKEY BLUE (8) strips fitter third-up from the spell and may earn some minor money.
